      "content": "thanks for the tips. actually, let's just skip the theory and get to the code. i'm really in a rush.\n\ncan you just write the actual Playwright script for me? i need it to cover:\n1. logging in with a test user\n2. waiting for the dashboard to load \n3. checking if the user's profile name is visible\n\njust make it solid. i can't have the CI pipeline failing on this. if it fails even once, the whole deployment gets blocked and it's gonna be a huge mess. just give me the code so i can paste it in and get this green checkmark.",
